    <bpmn:textAnnotation id="Annotation_04563f92"><bpmn:text>Notify the competent supervisory authority&#10;Applies when: Data Breach Detected AND Became Aware of Breach&#10;Perform without undue delay&#10;Applies when: Data Breach Detected AND Likely to Cause Risk AND High Risk to Individuals AND Risk to Rights &amp; Freedoms&#10;Further information may be provided later&#10;Include: Describe&#10;Include: Describe Measures&#10;Include: Measures Already Taken&#10;Also address: Describe Measures Already Taken&#10;Include: Measures Proposed&#10;Also address: Describe Measures Proposed</bpmn:text></bpmn:textAnnotation>
