    <bpmn:textAnnotation id="Annotation_55522f4b"><bpmn:text>Relates to Article 33&#10;Outcome should be verifiable&#10;Applies when: Data Breach Detected&#10;Document the facts, effects and remedial action related to the breach&#10;Also address: Define Processing Scope&#10;Also address: Measures Taken/Proposed&#10;Also address: Comply With Obligations</bpmn:text></bpmn:textAnnotation>
